    "test": {
      "builder": "@nrwl/jest:jest",
      "options": {
        "jestConfig": "apps/my-app/src/test/playwright.jest.config.js",
        "passWithNoTests": true
      },
      "outputs": ["{options.outputPath}"],
      "configurations": {
        "production": {
          "devServerTarget": "my-app:serve:production"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
This configuration creates a new project called `my-app-playwright` with a root directory of `apps/my-app/src/test`, and sets up Jest as the test runner. Note that this configuration assumes that you are using Jest as your test runner for your other tests.

