}
```
In this example, I have replaced the `h2` and `p` elements from the previous example with `Typography` components from Material-UI. The `variant` prop is used to set the text style, "h5" for name and "body1" for email.

I have also replaced the "Loading..." text with a `LinearProgress` component from Material-UI. This component is used to display a loading spinner while the data is being fetched.

