allprojects {
    repositories {
        maven { url "https://artifacts.castlabs.com/artifactory/castlabs" }
    }
}
```
And add it to your app level `build.gradle` file:
```python
dependencies {
    implementation "com.castlabs:castlabs-sdk:4.1.0"
}
```
1. Create an API service interface using Retrofit to make a GET request to the `/api/MediaStorage/GetCookies` endpoint and get the cookies. Here is an example of how you can create an ApiService interface:
```kotlin
